import React from 'react';

import img1 from './Treasure-hunt.jpeg';


import {ButtonGroup,ButtonToolbar,CardColumns,CardGroup,Card,Button,Container,Nav,Navbar,NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap';

import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import './Card.css';

const MyCards = (props) => {

  return(

    <Container className='mt-5' fluid="md">

      <CardGroup className='mt-5'>
        <CardColumns >

          <Card className='cardRounded'>
            <Card.Img className="cutomImgBase" variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" className='customRounded'/>
            <Card.Body >
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
                This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to
                additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
              </Card.Text>
              <Button className="customButton">Enter</Button>
            </Card.Body>

          </Card>
          <Card className='cardRounded'>
          <Card.Img variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" className='customRounded'/>
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
              This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to
              additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
              </Card.Text>
              <Button className="customButton">Enter</Button>
            </Card.Body>

          </Card>
          <Card className='cardRounded'>
          <Card.Img variant="top" src={img1} alt="Logo" className='customRounded'/>
            <Card.Body>
              <Card.Title>Card title</Card.Title>
              <Card.Text>
              This is a wider card with supporting text below as a natural lead-in to
              additional content. This content is a little bit longer.
              </Card.Text>
              <ButtonToolbar aria-label="Toolbar with button groups">
                <ButtonGroup className="me-2" aria-label="First group">
                  <Button className="tinyCustomButton">1</Button> <Button className="tinyCustomButton">2</Button> <Button className="tinyCustomButton">3</Button > <Button className="tinyCustomButton">4</Button>
                </ButtonGroup>

                <ButtonGroup className="me-2" aria-label="Second group">
                  <Button className="tinyCustomButton">5</Button > <Button className="tinyCustomButton">6</Button> <Button className="tinyCustomButton">7</Button>
                </ButtonGroup>

                <ButtonGroup aria-label="Third group">

                </ButtonGroup>
              </ButtonToolbar>
            </Card.Body>

          </Card>
          </CardColumns>
      </CardGroup>
    </Container>


  );


};

export default MyCards;
